PrecisAmendment to the NATIONAL PARKS GENERAL REGULATIONS (1) increasing some golfing fees at Cape Breton Highlands National Park and mooring fees at Terra Nova National Park between 5 and 10 percent to better reflect the level of service provided to bring them more in line with similar services provided by the private sector; and (2) introducing the daily rate for use of the facilities at the Miette Hot Springs at Jasper National Park; and (3) making a minor housekeeping amendment by changing the word "boat" to "watercraft".
